OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Fuel duty should be increased to fund  
OL,6, pothole repairs, the group representing
OL,7, councils in England and Wales has said.
OL,9,FThe Local Government Association (LGA) 
OL,10,Fsaid cuts to spending on tackling      
OL,11,Fpotholes are among the most severe out 
OL,12,Fof 13 major nations - with the UK's    
OL,13,Fspending halving in 13 years.          
OL,15,FIt puts the UK behind the US, Japan and
OL,16,FNew Zealand, which have upped spending.
OL,18,FThe government said it was spending    
OL,19,Fover #5bn in the five years to 2025 -  
OL,20,Fenough to fix "millions of potholes".  
